From cou.: 19 (3) a clear dependence of the yielding/gelating scenario, as reflected by the area of the hysteresis, on the degree of the steadiness of the external forcing, i.e. how fast is the external stress varied during the solid–fluid transition, see Fig. 3 and ref. 13 and 15 for a comprehensive discussion.
From Soup: 19 (3) a clear dependence of the yielding/gelating scenario, as reflected by the area of the hysteresis, on the degree of the steadiness of the external forcing, i.e. how fast is the external stress varied during the solid–fluid transition, see Fig. 3 and ref. 13 and 15 for a comprehensive discussion.
