From cou.: 28 The paper is organized as follows. The mathematical formulation of the model and the simulation algorithm are presented in Section 2 with details in the Appendix. The results of the simulations according to the microscopic model are presented in Section 3. The paper concludes in Section 4 with a discussion of the main findings and their possible implications and extensions.
From Soup: 28 The paper is organized as follows. The mathematical formulation of the model and the simulation algorithm are presented in Section 2 with details in the Appendix. The results of the simulations according to the microscopic model are presented in Section 3. The paper concludes in Section 4 with a discussion of the main findings and their possible implications and extensions.
