From Soup: 226 In this Section we mainly obtain various insights about the macroscopic behaviour of our model based on Monte Carlo simulations from Algorithms 1 and 2 and make some comparisons with both existing theoretical results and the qualitative yielding behaviour observed in macroscopic experiments. The analysis will be carried on as a function of the applied stress σ , site specific threshold α and the interaction parameter β .
